DATABASE MODELS

User Model:

memberId (unique)
username (unique)
name
email (unique)
password
events [
{
name
date
}
]

Event Model:

eventId (auto-generated like EVT001)
title
date
attendees [
User ObjectId
]

WORKING BACKEND FEATURES

User registration

POST
/api/auth/register

Fields:
memberId
username
name
email
password

User login

POST
/api/auth/login

Fields:
username
password

Returns JWT token.

Auth middleware

Authorization header format:

Bearer TOKEN

Create event

POST
/api/events/create

Body:
title
date

eventId auto-generated.

Mark attendance

POST
/api/events/attendance

Body:
eventId
memberId

Process:

1. Find event
2. Find user
3. Add user to event.attendees
4. Add event to user.events timeline

